{"tid":2103081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔記得帶地址證明或者搵唔到嘅，可以上番ebanking睇月結單","createTime":"2020-07-11T03:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T04:38:34.000Z","uid":26087,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"af9be8a82925fd1ff67605b2e8b16e2df6588315","tid":2103081,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"身邊有啲朋友真係無乜有信寄比佢，加上而家乜都轉嗮email寄比你。後生果批直情基本上無信會寄比你。<br />\n<br />\n請打開你地嘅ebanking，搵番check月結單果頁果到一定有你嘅住址證明<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">今日要出街玩嘅又好有要做都好，全部都麻煩投完票先去做去玩！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdcaf983f8b6015a577c8ae35c561bce0d3df61","tid":2103081,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"投票投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b779d66179adcf9710806ecf9d7fe70f26a151","tid":2103081,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"星期日係咪都得?"},{"pid":"8fbbf25ba058e3bd3bad5c19a713cb5b80279ccf","tid":2103081,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78630c978b82ac17d4c2367d52111429f608c022","tid":2103081,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b779d66179adcf9710806ecf9d7fe70f26a151","tid":2103081,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"星期日係咪都得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"係，一連兩日<br />\n<br />\n今日要番工嘅唔緊要，聽日都可以投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d932348108dbcbfcd49420d740abe8f00b576c6","tid":2103081,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"唔好最後一刻先投<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加快投票流程步驟, 避免輪到你先黎搞造成阻礙<br />\n<br />\n1.睇自己準備去邊個地方投, 再搵返個票站編號<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw%2Fview&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ecd48162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rTHp9g2UfTax1rQMgJEyQ6CEjHdJUXHw/view</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 入去依度輸入票站個號碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebapp.popvote.hk%2Fonboarding&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=212d23e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webapp.popvote.hk/onboarding</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 拎到個QR CODE之後再screen capture , save低<br />\n<br />\n4. 之後再帶住址證明+screen capture+身分證<br />\n去1.揀左嘅票站投票"},{"pid":"b3491a033c2d21cbe44ba4cb18eddfba11a2f1f6","tid":2103081,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"突然間唔好意思比職員知仲用緊支銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d40ce92ea12b7864bb17d86a432380e6d88e33","tid":2103081,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://landing.popvote.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flanding.popvote.hk%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=f2266a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://landing.popvote.hk/</a><br />\n推Link"},{"pid":"433ab908b9a0e2a51685f5ef2df41361ceeaac0b","tid":2103081,"uid":26087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3491a033c2d21cbe44ba4cb18eddfba11a2f1f6","tid":2103081,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"突然間唔好意思比職員知仲用緊支銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"見到你去投票人地都唔知幾咁開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f90f8e88