ps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7wHq4G.png&h=ad5cd19d&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n若果係 &quot;傳統功能界別&quot; 選民， 就答 &quot;是&quot;<br />\n若果係 &quot;超級區議會&quot; 界別選民 ，就答 &quot;否&quot;<br />\n<br />\n身份證簽發日期<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yef1GOj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyef1GOj.jpg&h=10b6a0d8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">3. 拎到個QR CODE之後再screen capture , save低</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">4. <span class=\"green\"><span class=\"x-large\">！未完成！</span></span><br />\n要帶住址證明+screen capture+身分證，去1.揀左嘅票站投票</span></strong>"}]}